        "en": "GOV.UK requires successful completion of a UK bachelor’s degree, postgraduate degree, or other eligible course studied for a minimum period with a Student or Tier 4 visa. Your provider must report completion to the Home Office.",
        "zh-Hans": "GOV.UK 要求成功完成英国学士、研究生或其他合资格课程，并在学生或 Tier 4 签证下学习达到最短期限。教育机构必须向内政部报告完成情况。"
      }
