      "en": "GOV.UK says you usually get a decision within 8 weeks after applying online, proving identity, and providing documents. You must apply from inside the UK before your Student or Tier 4 visa expires. You cannot extend a Graduate visa.",
      "zh-Hans": "GOV.UK 说明在线申请、完成身份证明并提交文件后通常 8 周内出结果。必须在英国境内、并在学生或 Tier 4 签证到期前申请。毕业签证不可延期。"
    },
